name: Spring Nap [detail]
description: Detail of Spring Nap by Chiara Magni - "Creativity and being able to express one's emotions through a canvas and color is something very similar to magic. Creating an emotion from nothing is truly something unique." - Chiara Magni is an Italian painter from Lake Garda, Italy. She is the pioneer of a new Expressionist movement she has named "Bright Expressionism". Chiara Magni was featured in several publications like "The World Of Interiors" and "Vogue".
